  "title": "Senior/ Staff Nurse (Endoscopy) - Hospital, On-call [GC]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job description</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Assist with the clinic’s daily operations and overall activities.</li><li><p>Provide basic nursing support and assist with patient care.</p></li><li><p>Support endoscopy procedures as required.</p></li><li><p>Assist the Medical Director with duties at the assigned clinic.</p></li><li><p>Handle customer service tasks such as cashiering, appointment scheduling, and answering patient enquiries.</p></li><li><p>Manage matters related to insurance, Medisave claims, and Letters of Guarantee.</p></li><li><p>Communicate with patients, vendors, suppliers, and regulatory authorities when needed.</p></li><li><p>Assist with the renewal of clinic licenses and required documentation.</p></li><li><p>Perform any other duties assigned by the Medical Director.<br /><br /><br />We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p></li></ul>",
